Starscream

He closed the cockpit as he got KitKat's message.

"No prob. Drillbit's a bit hurt, so get a CR Chamber ready for him. 
We're on the way."

Starscream takes off towards the base. On the way he breaks the news 
to Drillbit.

"Phobia was killed."
